1
00:01:07,280 --> 00:01:07,840
Black Street

2
00:01:08,040 --> 00:01:08,920
Infamous.

3
00:01:09,359 --> 00:01:10,000
People say

4
00:01:10,400 --> 00:01:12,519
the world's most vicious criminals live here.

5
00:01:12,879 --> 00:01:13,640
Murder, arson,

6
00:01:13,920 --> 00:01:14,599
every evil imaginable.

7
00:01:15,079 --> 00:01:15,799
Or rather,

8
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:17,040
the Black Street of the past

9
00:01:17,200 --> 00:01:18,000
used to be like that.

10
00:01:18,280 --> 00:01:19,760
Until a group of homeless

11
00:01:19,920 --> 00:01:20,959
masters seeking seclusion

12
00:01:21,280 --> 00:01:22,079
discovered this place,

13
00:01:22,519 --> 00:01:23,799
wiped out those villains,

14
00:01:24,040 --> 00:01:24,959
and took over their nest.

15
00:01:25,159 --> 00:01:27,359
Outsiders still avoid Black Street.

16
00:01:27,920 --> 00:01:28,879
So these people play along,

17
00:01:29,239 --> 00:01:30,640
putting on vicious faces

18
00:01:30,959 --> 00:01:31,840
just for some peace and quiet.

19
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:32,879
No one bothers anyone.

20
00:01:32,959 --> 00:01:33,599
As for me,

21
00:01:33,959 --> 00:01:34,719
my name is Su Yang.

22
00:01:35,120 --> 00:01:36,040
They call me

23
00:01:36,439 --> 00:01:37,079
Madman.

24
00:01:37,359 --> 00:01:39,439
Half a spoon of salt fell into the pot.

25
00:01:40,680 --> 00:01:42,680
That dream is still bothering you.

26
00:01:43,239 --> 00:01:44,480
Tormenting me, more like.

27
00:01:55,159 --> 00:01:56,159
What did you just say?

28
00:01:56,959 --> 00:01:57,599
I said...

29
00:01:57,840 --> 00:01:58,439
Never mind.

30
00:01:59,359 --> 00:02:01,359
So you're leaving Black Street to...?

31
00:02:01,480 --> 00:02:02,400
To verify something.

32
00:02:04,159 --> 00:02:05,959
Even if the verification proves

33
00:02:06,400 --> 00:02:07,680
the dream is real,

34
00:02:08,120 --> 00:02:09,240
what can you do about it?

35
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:10,360
Obviously...

36
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:21,319
What is that?

37
00:02:22,199 --> 00:02:22,879
I...

38
00:02:22,879 --> 00:02:23,759
I have to record this!

39
00:02:23,759 --> 00:02:24,319
Look, look!

40
00:02:25,439 --> 00:02:26,560
I got it on camera, look!

41
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:27,159
Hurry, record it!

42
00:02:27,560 --> 00:02:28,039
Quick, take a picture!

43
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:30,400
See the Celestial Palace in the sky?

44
00:02:31,080 --> 00:02:31,719
Look, look!

45
00:02:31,879 --> 00:02:32,960
Look, there are Immortals!

46
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:35,000
Can we cultivate immortality now?

47
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:35,599
Is this for real?

48
00:02:35,599 --> 00:02:36,360
Hurry, record it!

49
00:02:37,439 --> 00:02:39,680
Who are you playing the good student for?

50
00:02:39,680 --> 00:02:41,919
Think you can get close to Chu Lingling?

51
00:02:42,520 --> 00:02:43,800
Come on, record this clearly!

52
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:46,759
Come on!

53
00:03:02,039 --> 00:03:03,199
I've never seen anything like this.

54
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:05,520
Am I seeing this right?

55
00:03:12,319 --> 00:03:14,560
Today I become an Immortal,

56
00:03:17,120 --> 00:03:18,400
treading upon the Ninth Heaven,

57
00:03:18,479 --> 00:03:19,680
summoning lightning from all sides!

58
00:03:29,039 --> 00:03:30,039
Who told you to stand up?

59
00:03:30,159 --> 00:03:31,000
Get back down!

60
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:35,159
The green lamp, ever by my side.

61
00:03:35,479 --> 00:03:36,520
A giant axe splits the mountain.

62
00:03:37,919 --> 00:03:39,120
The path to immortality stretches far.

63
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:40,719
Descending into the mortal world.

64
00:03:44,120 --> 00:03:46,039
Chenxiang splits the mountain!

65
00:04:11,199 --> 00:04:12,360
Starting today,

66
00:04:12,840 --> 00:04:14,039
no one can bully me.

67
00:04:14,319 --> 00:04:15,199
No one at all.

68
00:04:16,360 --> 00:04:17,319
A thousand years ago,

69
00:04:17,720 --> 00:04:20,240
the Celestial Realm faced the Great Tribulation of Inner Demons.

70
00:04:20,439 --> 00:04:22,839
Countless Immortals fell into madness

71
00:04:22,959 --> 00:04:24,360
and slaughtered each other,

72
00:04:24,439 --> 00:04:27,240
causing the Celestial Realm to collapse.

73
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:29,480
Great Tribulation of Inner Demons.

74
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:32,160
Calamity born of the heart.

75
00:04:32,160 --> 00:04:33,399
Tribulation, my ass.

76
00:04:33,600 --> 00:04:35,319
If we die, we die together.

77
00:04:35,480 --> 00:04:37,240
The Immortals lost much of their power,

78
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:40,360
losing control over the mortal world.

79
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:42,079
To survive this, the Immortal Emperor

80
00:04:42,519 --> 00:04:43,759
expended his essence

81
00:04:44,360 --> 00:04:46,720
to set up eight sealing gates,

82
00:04:46,959 --> 00:04:48,839
sealing all Immortals within.

83
00:04:49,720 --> 00:04:51,519
He then sent word to all Immortals:

84
00:04:52,160 --> 00:04:54,759
In a millennium, when inner demons fade,

85
00:04:55,639 --> 00:04:58,040
only a mortal bearing the Celestial Seed,

86
00:04:58,360 --> 00:05:00,920
opening the 8 Immortal-Sealing Gates,

87
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:04,879
can the Celestial Realm regain control.

88
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:18,680
Do you believe that in this world,

89
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:20,519
Immortals really speak through dreams?

90
00:05:21,319 --> 00:05:21,959
I do.

91
00:05:24,319 --> 00:05:24,920
No.

92
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:26,560
You don't.

93
00:05:31,199 --> 00:05:32,720
What are you trying to say?

94
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:36,319
I often have this dream.

95
00:05:38,839 --> 00:05:39,879
Coincidentally,

96
00:05:42,199 --> 00:05:43,480
the scene in the dream

97
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:45,360
and this place

98
00:05:45,959 --> 00:05:46,839
are identical.

99
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:50,240
A robber

100
00:05:50,399 --> 00:05:52,240
killed a psychiatrist,

101
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:53,800
and hid the body

102
00:05:54,279 --> 00:05:55,439
inside the bathroom.

103
00:06:02,519 --> 00:06:04,639
Who the hell are you?

104
00:06:09,839 --> 00:06:11,040
Who I am doesn't matter.

105
00:06:11,639 --> 00:06:12,439
It's just that

106
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:13,920
in ten more seconds,

107
00:06:14,519 --> 00:06:15,759
this robber

108
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:18,079
will be hit by a car and killed.

109
00:06:20,800 --> 00:06:21,519
If

110
00:06:22,079 --> 00:06:23,279
you aren't killed,

111
00:06:23,399 --> 00:06:24,360
then that proves

112
00:06:24,560 --> 00:06:25,480
it was all just a dream.

113
00:06:25,879 --> 00:06:26,480
You...

114
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:32,199
Listen.

115
00:06:34,160 --> 00:06:34,920
Three.

116
00:06:36,160 --> 00:06:36,759
Two.

117
00:06:38,199 --> 00:06:38,639
One.

118
00:06:59,279 --> 00:06:59,959
Looks like

119
00:07:00,399 --> 00:07:01,240
this isn't a dream.

120
00:07:03,519 --> 00:07:05,439
So that bizarre, fantastical world

121
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:07,279
will eventually arrive.

122
00:07:12,639 --> 00:07:13,959
I can't wait.

123
00:07:14,519 --> 00:07:15,800
What happened?

124
00:07:16,600 --> 00:07:18,079
That's a serious crash!

125
00:07:18,439 --> 00:07:19,560
This guy's gotta be dead, right?

126
00:08:05,040 --> 00:08:05,920
Take a break.

127
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:07,800
Thanks.

128
00:08:10,720 --> 00:08:11,519
So,

129
00:08:11,720 --> 00:08:12,879
in your scenario,

130
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:14,800
what's the Immortals' true purpose?

131
00:08:17,319 --> 00:08:19,439
Ancient Immortals are about to descend,

132
00:08:19,720 --> 00:08:21,160
sowing Celestial Seeds among mortals.

133
00:08:21,439 --> 00:08:23,399
Everyone gets a chance at immortality.

134
00:08:23,879 --> 00:08:25,160
A heaven-sent temptation

135
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:27,639
slowly unfolds around Su Yang.

136
00:08:28,639 --> 00:08:29,639
But

137
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:32,600
the Celestial Realm controls mortals via blessings.

138
00:08:33,279 --> 00:08:35,279
As the Chosen One, Su Yang,

139
00:08:35,759 --> 00:08:37,000
how is he going to break through?

140
00:08:38,480 --> 00:08:39,120
Indeed.

141
00:08:42,240 --> 00:08:43,960
How will he break through?

142
00:08:50,679 --> 00:08:51,519
First,

143
00:08:52,679 --> 00:08:54,559
he needs to find that gate,

144
00:08:55,320 --> 00:08:58,039
a gate that can change the world.

145
00:09:03,639 --> 00:09:04,320
Unload the cargo.

146
00:09:04,480 --> 00:09:05,120
Six of them,

147
00:09:05,240 --> 00:09:06,120
all alive and kicking.

148
00:09:14,240 --> 00:09:14,960
What's going on?

149
00:09:21,159 --> 00:09:22,519
So it's here.

150
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:25,120
Exactly like in my dream.

151
00:09:25,919 --> 00:09:27,080
But many of the details

152
00:09:27,559 --> 00:09:28,360
I can't remember clearly.

153
00:09:29,559 --> 00:09:30,480
If you hadn't led the way,

154
00:09:30,600 --> 00:09:31,399
I'd never have found it.

155
00:09:31,679 --> 00:09:32,159
Thanks,

156
00:09:32,639 --> 00:09:33,080
big bro.

157
00:09:34,039 --> 00:09:34,639
Brother,

158
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:36,039
State your business.

159
00:09:36,679 --> 00:09:37,480
I live on Black Street.

160
00:09:37,840 --> 00:09:38,840
They all like to call me

161
00:09:38,960 --> 00:09:39,360
Madman.

162
00:09:41,120 --> 00:09:42,519
Bro, bro, bro!

163
00:09:42,600 --> 00:09:43,440
He says he's the Madman.

164
00:09:43,799 --> 00:09:44,320
What are you panicking for?

165
00:09:44,720 --> 00:09:45,960
You believe he's the Madman just like that?

166
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:47,120
Call the boss.

167
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:48,480
Have him send a photo of Madman. Go!

168
00:09:48,480 --> 00:09:49,360
Okay, okay, okay.

169
00:09:52,399 --> 00:09:52,919
Brother,

170
00:09:54,159 --> 00:09:55,799
though I've long admired the Madman,

171
00:09:56,279 --> 00:09:57,600
I've never actually met him.

172
00:09:58,080 --> 00:09:59,519
If someone were impersonating him

173
00:09:59,519 --> 00:10:00,639
and ruining his reputation,

174
00:10:00,759 --> 00:10:01,399
I think

175
00:10:01,480 --> 00:10:02,200
that wouldn't be right either.

176
00:10:02,720 --> 00:10:05,320
So could you prove your identity?

177
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:07,879
How do I prove it?

178
00:10:12,559 --> 00:10:13,320
Well then,

179
00:10:14,320 --> 00:10:15,320
let me show you some madness.

180
00:10:23,399 --> 00:10:23,960
Nobody move!

181
00:10:24,759 --> 00:10:25,200
Get back here.

182
00:10:33,200 --> 00:10:34,159
Is that proof enough?

183
00:10:34,559 --> 00:10:35,759
Even if you might not be the Madman,

184
00:10:37,320 --> 00:10:37,720
still,

185
00:10:38,360 --> 00:10:40,279
we still can't afford to mess with you.

186
00:10:40,279 --> 00:10:40,919
Suit yourself.

187
00:10:41,039 --> 00:10:41,960
Please, go right ahead.

188
00:10:41,960 --> 00:10:43,320
Bro, bro!

189
00:10:43,519 --> 00:10:44,240
Bro, bro!

190
00:10:44,320 --> 00:10:45,399
He really is the Madman.

191
00:10:50,960 --> 00:10:52,600
We brothers were in the wrong.

192
00:10:52,600 --> 00:10:53,320
We offended you.

193
00:10:53,679 --> 00:10:54,399
You...

194
00:10:57,039 --> 00:10:58,159
I need quiet.

195
00:10:58,159 --> 00:10:58,720
I get it.

196
00:10:59,039 --> 00:10:59,600
I get it.

197
00:11:00,279 --> 00:11:01,000
Brothers, let's go!

198
00:11:17,279 --> 00:11:19,000
It really is just like in my dream.

199
00:12:03,679 --> 00:12:04,840
In my dreams,

200
00:12:05,279 --> 00:12:07,399
this gate appears most often.

201
00:12:09,919 --> 00:12:11,600
So those seemingly prophetic dreams

202
00:12:12,559 --> 00:12:13,919
all came from you?

203
00:12:22,600 --> 00:12:23,440
Damn it.

204
00:12:23,639 --> 00:12:24,200
It's

205
00:12:25,679 --> 00:12:26,639
happening again.

206
00:13:03,799 --> 00:13:05,279
Push open this gate

207
00:13:05,799 --> 00:13:07,120
to become an Immortal,

208
00:13:07,279 --> 00:13:08,320
to live forever,

209
00:13:08,320 --> 00:13:10,159
to be eternal through the ages.

210
00:13:12,480 --> 00:13:13,840
So this is

211
00:13:15,919 --> 00:13:17,759
why you kept weaving dreams

212
00:13:17,919 --> 00:13:19,360
to lure me here?

213
00:13:22,720 --> 00:13:23,799
Becoming an Immortal

214
00:13:24,399 --> 00:13:26,159
seems like

215
00:13:26,879 --> 00:13:28,879
a pretty good path.

216
00:14:03,600 --> 00:14:05,519
I can almost feel your

217
00:14:06,000 --> 00:14:06,879
joy

218
00:14:07,600 --> 00:14:08,360
Becoming an Immortal.

219
00:14:09,600 --> 00:14:10,360
Eternal life.

220
00:14:13,799 --> 00:14:14,639
Do you know

221
00:14:15,120 --> 00:14:17,360
how much I hate having

222
00:14:18,000 --> 00:14:20,120
strange dreams while I sleep?

223
00:14:22,639 --> 00:14:23,840
Even opening the gate

224
00:14:25,159 --> 00:14:26,519
depends on my mood.

225
00:14:27,799 --> 00:14:29,960
Not having you pester me day and night.

226
00:14:31,039 --> 00:14:32,200
Finding you

227
00:14:32,480 --> 00:14:34,840
has wasted so much of my time.

228
00:14:41,279 --> 00:14:43,200
So you do bleed.

229
00:14:43,840 --> 00:14:44,600
An Immortal

230
00:14:45,039 --> 00:14:45,879
can feel pain too.

231
00:14:45,879 --> 00:14:47,919
The other seven Immortal Gates have risen.

232
00:14:48,279 --> 00:14:49,679
If the main gate doesn't rise soon,

233
00:14:50,039 --> 00:14:51,559
calamity will descend.

234
00:14:51,559 --> 00:14:53,759
You're playing with fire.

235
00:14:53,919 --> 00:14:55,799
Would you ignore the future?

236
00:14:56,159 --> 00:14:57,919
If you could really foresee the future,

237
00:14:58,519 --> 00:14:59,879
you definitely wouldn't have chosen me.

238
00:15:00,480 --> 00:15:01,720
Because in this life,

239
00:15:02,039 --> 00:15:02,919
what I hate most

240
00:15:03,080 --> 00:15:04,919
is being threatened.

241
00:15:38,120 --> 00:15:39,039
Possession,

242
00:15:40,159 --> 00:15:41,000
body-snatching,

243
00:15:41,799 --> 00:15:42,960
or a curse?

244
00:15:44,279 --> 00:15:45,879
If destroying you were easy,

245
00:15:46,039 --> 00:15:47,360
that'd be too boring.

246
00:15:48,279 --> 00:15:49,159
This is just right.

247
00:15:51,240 --> 00:15:52,639
We can take our time.

248
00:16:01,840 --> 00:16:02,480
Hurry up!

249
00:16:04,200 --> 00:16:05,600
He's back! He's back!

250
00:16:05,799 --> 00:16:06,919
The monkey isn't untied yet.

251
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:08,000
Forget the damn monkey!

252
00:16:08,000 --> 00:16:08,679
Just run!

253
00:16:08,879 --> 00:16:09,399
Move!
